track_notes: I followed Google map to Yakima Rim trail parking(also known as Yakima Skyline trail).  The last few miles were on a gravel road, but I made it fine in car.  Total hike ~10.3 miles and 2,572 feet of gain.  Tim KG7EJT has also hiked starting at 46.7352, -120.4938 which cuts 1,000 feet of gain and approximately 5 miles from the hike! Thank you to input from Josh WU7H that this can be a near drive up with high clearance vehicle, and paired with Rattler Benchmark W7W/MC-058 (comments in YouTube video)
track_title: Yakima Rim trail to Gracie Point
